ine/.highlight/israel-hamas-war-what-if-theres-another-way-to-fight-fundamentalism/0000018b-da13-df9a-ab8b-dedba7c10000</link><description>西方工具可以战胜原教旨主义和恐怖主义的幻想已经彻底破灭。鉴于左派知识分子的虚伪和右派对战争的渴望，也许是时候寻求新的方法了</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 23:52:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israel-hamas-war-what-if-theres-another-way-to-fight-fundamentalism/0000018b-da13-df9a-ab8b-dedba7c10000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡正在尝试，但将加沙的灾难归咎于国防机构并不容易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-trying-but-pinning-gaza-debacle-on-the-defense-establishment-wont-be-easy/0000018b-da6c-d168-a3ef-dffebe3d0000</link><description>在让他的朝臣在腐败案件中对抗检察官和警方调查人员后，内塔尼亚胡将希望给予以色列安全部门负责人同样的待遇。利库德集团的一名高级官员已经开始收集针对军事情报局局长的信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 23:35:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-trying-but-pinning-gaza-debacle-on-the-defense-establishment-wont-be-easy/0000018b-da6c-d168-a3ef-dffebe3d0000</guid></item><item><title>欧盟高级外交官：哈马斯将失去加沙，红十字会必须进入以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/top-european-diplomat-hamas-will-lose-gaza-red-cross-must-get-access-to-israeli-hostages/0000018b-d9db-df9a-ab8b-dfdbace10000</link><description>欧盟外交部长何塞普·博雷尔访问了以色列南部的贝埃里基布兹，哈马斯于 10 月 7 日在那里杀害了 100 多名居民</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 23:13:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/top-european-diplomat-hamas-will-lose-gaza-red-cross-must-get-access-to-israeli-hostages/0000018b-d9db-df9a-ab8b-dfdbace10000</guid></item><item><title>美国参议员如何在以色列和加沙问题上达成民主党和犹太人的共识</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/how-a-u-s-senator-captured-the-democratic-and-jewish-center-on-israel-and-gaza/0000018b-da25-d168-a3ef-dfffb4140000</link><description>来自格鲁吉亚的犹太参议员乔恩·奥索夫 (Jon Ossoff) 连贯、清晰地表达了三个可以共存的想法：哈马斯的袭击显然是错误的，以色列有权以武力回应以保护自己，加沙无辜的巴勒斯坦平民应该受到惩罚。保护</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 22:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/how-a-u-s-senator-captured-the-democratic-and-jewish-center-on-israel-and-gaza/0000018b-da25-d168-a3ef-dfffb4140000</guid></item><item><title>数千人参加被杀的加拿大以色列和平活动家维维安·西尔弗的葬礼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/thousands-attend-funeral-of-slain-canadian-israeli-peace-activist-vivian-silver/0000018b-d9cd-d423-affb-fbef6e360000</link><description>以色列社会各界人士前来向西尔弗告别，西尔弗于 10 月 7 日在贝埃里基布兹的家中被哈马斯杀害。“你知道，我们说希伯来语还是阿拉伯语并不重要，这并不重要。”无论我们是出生在加沙边境还是加沙地带，你都知道我们的未来是紧密相连的。”和平活动家加迪尔·哈尼 (Ghadir Hani) 说道</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 21:38:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/thousands-attend-funeral-of-slain-canadian-israeli-peace-activist-vivian-silver/0000018b-d9cd-d423-affb-fbef6e360000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军宣布，在加沙 Al-Shifa 医院附近发现了 65 岁以色列人质尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/body-of-65-year-old-israeli-woman-hostage-found-near-gazas-al-shifa-hospital/0000018b-d991-d168-a3ef-ddfb78ce0000</link><description>以色列士兵在大型医疗中心附近进行地面行动时发现了尸体，以色列国防军称哈马斯将其用作指挥中心</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 20:41:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/body-of-65-year-old-israeli-woman-hostage-found-near-gazas-al-shifa-hospital/0000018b-d991-d168-a3ef-ddfb78ce0000</guid></item><item><title>绝食的以色列拉比：“人质没有接受红十字会探视，这太疯狂了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-rabbi-on-hunger-strike-insane-that-hostages-havent-received-a-red-cross-visit/0000018b-d8d0-df9a-ab8b-ded860090000</link><description>拉比阿维丹·弗里德曼现已绝食一周，呼吁以色列阻止人道主义援助进入加沙，直到红十字会获准接触被哈马斯扣押的 239 名以色列人质。他说：“人道主义援助需要面向全人类，我们的孩子也同样是人。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 20:39:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-rabbi-on-hunger-strike-insane-that-hostages-havent-received-a-red-cross-visit/0000018b-d8d0-df9a-ab8b-ded860090000</guid></item><item><title>从以色列国防军到孤立：以色列正统派如何应对哈马斯大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/from-idf-to-isolation-how-israels-haredim-are-responding-to-the-hamas-massacre/0000018b-d955-d423-affb-fbf787610000</link><description>该国现在有几个不同的极端正统派社区，其分歧不是由旧的宗教联系造成的，而是由每个群体的“以色列化”程度造成的</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 20:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/from-idf-to-isolation-how-israels-haredim-are-responding-to-the-hamas-massacre/0000018b-d955-d423-affb-fbf787610000</guid></item><item><title>为什么奥萨马·本·拉登在 TikTok 上走红？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-16/ty-article/.highlight/why-is-osama-bin-laden-going-viral-on-tiktok/0000018b-d94b-df9a-ab8b-dfcb3a530000</link><description>奥萨马·本·拉登 (Osama bin Laden) 在 TikTok 上很火爆，你可以责怪犹太人（就像他那样）</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 20:02:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-16/ty-article/.highlight/why-is-osama-bin-laden-going-viral-on-tiktok/0000018b-d94b-df9a-ab8b-dfcb3a530000</guid></item><item><title>有多少以色列人死亡？考古学家共同努力寻找人类遗骸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/archaeologists-assist-in-locating-human-remains-after-hamas-attacks/0000018b-d930-d168-a3ef-ddfa00260000</link><description>哈马斯的袭击造成了多少谋杀受害者、阵亡士兵、失踪人员和人质？一队考古学家来到加沙边境附近的基布兹尼尔奥兹，协助修复被烧毁的房屋</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 17:54:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/archaeologists-assist-in-locating-human-remains-after-hamas-attacks/00